# Project Codex Agents

This directory is for repository-scoped Codex custom agents that are safe to
track with the project.

Use it only for roles that encode durable project behavior. Keep private,
workstation-specific, customer-specific, and secret-bearing role definitions in
ignored local overlay files.

## Install Pattern

Preview first:

```bash
export DEV_SKILLS="$dev_skills_path"
python3 "$DEV_SKILLS/subagents/hardened-codex/scripts/sync_agents.py" \
  --overlay tooling \
  --project-dir "$PWD" \
  --dry-run
```

Apply only after reviewing the planned copy actions:

```bash
python3 "$DEV_SKILLS/subagents/hardened-codex/scripts/sync_agents.py" \
  --overlay tooling \
  --project-dir "$PWD"
```

Generated from `$pack_name` for `$repo_name`.
